{"tid":1902920,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦將痛失今屆英超冠軍！","createTime":"2020-02-28T15:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T15:52:12.000Z","uid":191921,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7748728fdbaff40a6f26f2eb23dd5fecbd7e7c0a","tid":1902920,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"《每日電訊報》報導，如因新冠病毒影響導致英超縮短賽程，利物浦不能拿到冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n同樣，聯賽后三名是否還會被降級，也無法得到保證，因為降級關係到數億英鎊的損失。<br />\n<br />\n因為武肺病毒的傳播，政府會取消未來至少2個月的各種體育賽事，這也意味著被叫停的比賽可能永遠不會再次舉行。<br />\n<br />\n在1939-1940賽季，英格蘭頂級聯賽只進行了三場比賽，就因二戰爆發而被取消，當時的黑池在頂級聯賽中排名第一，領先第二1分。"},{"pid":"4309cc870bdd288a0f42355194c80b1a5b07df54","tid":1902920,"uid":184827,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"逼害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5362d467037f7d597196f5547046f383d16d678","tid":1902920,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:39:09.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"cd65ee55bd6df63b127a5f84424877db026a367e","tid":1902920,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:39:21.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"84c83e6e66fd2435401d8d7fe9164f8a5b0b7f40","tid":1902920,"uid":33441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"唔分頭4名下屆歐聯都唔撚駛踢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c501371cbc52d8ba1a6481d37367309156aed1","tid":1902920,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/football/2016/04/04/celebs_liverpool_bus_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqEDjTm7JpzhSGR1_8ApEWQA1vLvhkMtVb21dMmpQBfEs.jpg?imwidth=450\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih